DRType

The Argonaut DocumentReferences Type Value Set is a 'starter set' of categorie supported for fetching and storing clinical notes.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://fhir.org/guides/argonaut-clinicalnotes/CodeSystem/dr-category
